3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Clea: I've come to deliver the fragrant fish sauce.

Owner, Tokyo: It was really good to rely on Dokusa-kun. I
never expected him to find such a rare item among rare
items.

Clea: Is it really that rare? I smelled it, but I didn't
feel anything special.

Owner, Tokyo: When was that!? If you smell it without
cooking it... ugh!?

Restaurant Miro's Chef: Thank you for helping. It's
unfortunate that the owner collapsed on a day like this.

Restaurant Miro's Chef: 'If this gets known by Gnil, I
wonder what will happen...'

Clea: If you're in trouble, please let me know. There might
be something I can help with.

Restaurant Miro's Chef: Gnil holds a grudge against the
owner because he was embarrassed at the party.

Restaurant Miro's Chef: That man came in smiling and is
currently enjoying a meal in the VIP room on the second
floor.
Clea: You think there's some ulterior motive, don't you?

Restaurant Miro's Chef: In addition, the owner collapsed and
today's main dish remains unfinished...

Restaurant Miro's Chef: It's frustrating, but as a gourmet,
Gnil is an excellent man who will surely spread rumors that
the taste of Restaurant Miro has declined.

Clea: I understand. We should investigate his intentions for
not eating the main dish, right?

Restaurant Miro's Chef: That may be so... but is it
possible?

Clea: I will give it a try. Please leave the preparation of
the main dish to me.

Owner, Tokyo. I had a bout of my chronic illness, but I'm
relieved. Also, I heard about the incident with Gnil from
the cook.

Clea: I heard that the cooking association in the empire is
ruled by Lord Baal.

Owner, Tokyo. I can't believe it's Baal...! So, handing over
Gnil was also for the purpose of reconnaissance!

Owner, Tokyo. I apologize for getting excited on my own, but
Baal, who was an excellent cook, is a man who was expelled
from the cooking association.

Owner, Tokyo. Revenge against the main cooking
association... He must have joined the underground cooking
association for that purpose.

Clea: An underground cooking association... I didn't know
such a thing existed.

Owner, Tokyo. A cooking showdown between the front and
back... Baal will do whatever it takes to win.

Owner, Tokyo. At that time, I want you to contact me through
a reliable channel like Kanonas, who I can trust, and make a
formal request.
